      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and it looks just as gorgeous as the day I bought it! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel inside and out. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been cared for with a ton of love, this is definitely the one. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out!",
