    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle is in pristine condition, featuring a deep metallic exterior finish that retains a mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and unscuffed, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a meticulous, full-service history and a drive that is exceptionally tight and responsive. Always garage-kept under a soft cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents a rare opportunity to own a truly flawless piece of automotive engineering.",
